{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "trmzgqgqyms",
    "category": "news",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=trMzgQGQYMs",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This game is so fun. I love the show.",
      "zh": "這遊戲真有趣。我喜歡這個節目。",
      "ja": "このゲームはとても楽しい。私はこの番組が大好きです。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's nice and cozy tonight.",
      "zh": "今晚很舒適溫馨。",
      "ja": "今夜は快適で居心地がいいです。",
      "time": "00:00:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The weather forecast says a storm is coming.",
      "zh": "天氣預報說有暴風雨要來了。",
      "ja": "天気予報では嵐が来ると言っています。",
      "time": "00:00:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A storm? Should we be worried?",
      "zh": "暴風雨？我們應該擔心嗎？",
      "ja": "嵐？心配するべきですか？",
      "time": "00:00:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, just some thunder and rain. We'll be fine.",
      "zh": "不，只是一些雷聲和雨。我們會沒事的。",
      "ja": "いいえ、ただの雷と雨です。大丈夫ですよ。",
      "time": "00:00:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What was that sound?",
      "zh": "那是什麼聲音？",
      "ja": "あの音は何？",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just thunder, sweetie, the storm is starting.",
      "zh": "只是雷聲，親愛的，暴風雨開始了。",
      "ja": "ただの雷よ、かわい子ちゃん、嵐が始まっているの。",
      "time": "00:00:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah!",
      "zh": "啊！",
      "ja": "あっ！",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom, Dad, I can't see anything.",
      "zh": "媽媽，爸爸，我什麼都看不到。",
      "ja": "ママ、パパ、何も見えないよ。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Everyone stay calm. Don't move.",
      "zh": "大家保持冷靜。不要動。",
      "ja": "みんな落ち着いて。動かないで。",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mommy, I'm scared.",
      "zh": "媽媽，我害怕。",
      "ja": "ママ、怖いよ。",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm right here, Lily. Stay calm.",
      "zh": "我就在這裡，莉莉。保持冷靜。",
      "ja": "ここにいるよ、リリー。落ち着いて。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm here, baby. Stay where you are.",
      "zh": "我在這裡，寶貝。待在原地。",
      "ja": "ここにいるよ、ベイビー。そこにいてね。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "John? I'm getting the flashlight. Hold on.",
      "zh": "約翰？我去拿手電筒。等一下。",
      "ja": "ジョン？懐中電灯を取ってくるね。待ってて。",
      "time": "00:00:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why is everything dark? What happened?",
      "zh": "為什麼一切都黑了？發生什麼事了？",
      "ja": "なぜ全部暗いの？何があったの？",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The power went out.",
      "zh": "停電了。",
      "ja": "停電したんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's okay.",
      "zh": "沒關係。",
      "ja": "大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't like the sun.",
      "zh": "我不喜歡太陽。",
      "ja": "太陽が好きじゃない。",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's okay, Lily. We're all here together.",
      "zh": "沒關係，莉莉。我們都在一起。",
      "ja": "大丈夫だよ、リリー。みんな一緒にいるから。",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why? I can see now.",
      "zh": "為什麼？我現在能看見了。",
      "ja": "なぜ？今見えるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why did the power go out?",
      "zh": "為什麼會停電？",
      "ja": "なぜ停電したの？",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The storm probably knocked out the electricity.",
      "zh": "可能是暴風雨造成停電。",
      "ja": "嵐が電気を止めたんだと思う。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "When will it come back?",
      "zh": "什麼時候會恢復？",
      "ja": "いつ戻るの？",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I don't know. Maybe a few hours.",
      "zh": "我不知道。可能幾個小時。",
      "ja": "わからない。多分数時間かな。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A few hours, but my tablet is dying.",
      "zh": "幾個小時，但我的平板快沒電了。",
      "ja": "数時間だけど、僕のタブレットがもうすぐ切れそう。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I can't watch my show.",
      "zh": "而且我不能看我的節目。",
      "ja": "それに番組も見れない。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We'll be okay without screens for a while.",
      "zh": "沒有螢幕一陣子也沒關係。",
      "ja": "しばらく画面なしでも大丈夫だよ。",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But will we do? We'll find something fun.",
      "zh": "我們會怎麼做？我們會找到有趣的事。",
      "ja": "でもどうする？楽しいことを見つけよう。",
      "time": "00:01:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's find candles first.",
      "zh": "先找蠟燭。",
      "ja": "まずはキャンドルを探そう。",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Then we'll think of something fun.",
      "zh": "然後我們再想有趣的事。",
      "ja": "それから楽しいことを考えよう。",
      "time": "00:01:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "These will help us see.",
      "zh": "這些會幫助我們看見。",
      "ja": "これで見えるようになるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Pretty. Like birthday candles.",
      "zh": "漂亮。像生日蠟燭。",
      "ja": "きれい。誕生日のキャンドルみたい。",
      "time": "00:01:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We have enough light now. See? It's cozy.",
      "zh": "我們現在有足夠的光了。看吧？很溫馨。",
      "ja": "もう十分な明かりがあるよ。ほら、居心地いいでしょ。",
      "time": "00:01:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But it's still scary. Everything looks different.",
      "zh": "但還是有點可怕。一切看起來不一樣。",
      "ja": "でもまだ怖い。全部違って見える。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Different can be an adventure.",
      "zh": "不同也可以是冒險。",
      "ja": "違うことは冒険になりうるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "An adventure?",
      "zh": "冒險？",
      "ja": "冒険？",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, let's pretend we're camping inside.",
      "zh": "是的，我們假裝在室內露營。",
      "ja": "そう、室内キャンプをしているふりをしよう。",
      "time": "00:01:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Indoor camping?",
      "zh": "室內露營？",
      "ja": "室内キャンプ？",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Why not? We have no power, so let's make it fun.",
      "zh": "為什麼不呢？沒電了，我們來玩得開心點。",
      "ja": "いいじゃない？電気がないから楽しくしよう。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like camping. We too.",
      "zh": "我喜歡露營。我們也是。",
      "ja": "キャンプが好き。私たちも。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's a great idea.",
      "zh": "這主意很好。",
      "ja": "いいアイデアだね。",
      "time": "00:02:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What do we do first?",
      "zh": "我們先做什麼？",
      "ja": "まず何をする？",
      "time": "00:02:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah, adventure.",
      "zh": "是啊，冒險。",
      "ja": "うん、冒険だ。",
      "time": "00:02:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's get started.",
      "zh": "我們開始吧。",
      "ja": "始めよう。",
      "time": "00:02:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Watch this.",
      "zh": "看這個。",
      "ja": "これを見て。",
      "time": "00:02:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A bunny on the wall.",
      "zh": "牆上的兔子。",
      "ja": "壁にウサギがいる。",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How did you do that?",
      "zh": "你怎麼做到的？",
      "ja": "どうやってやったの？",
      "time": "00:02:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's a shadow puppet.",
      "zh": "這是影子戲法。",
      "ja": "影絵だよ。",
      "time": "00:02:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Want to try?",
      "zh": "想試試嗎？",
      "ja": "やってみたい？",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Like this?",
      "zh": "像這樣？",
      "ja": "こんな感じ？",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A bird. I want to try.",
      "zh": "一隻鳥。我想試試。",
      "ja": "鳥だ。やってみたい。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let me help you.",
      "zh": "讓我幫你。",
      "ja": "手伝ってあげる。",
      "time": "00:02:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Put your hands like this.",
      "zh": "把手這樣放。",
      "ja": "手をこうやって置いて。",
      "time": "00:02:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look, a butterfly.",
      "zh": "看，一隻蝴蝶。",
      "ja": "見て、蝶々だよ。",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is actually fun.",
      "zh": "這真的很好玩。",
      "ja": "これは本当に楽しい。",
      "time": "00:02:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See? We don't need tablets for fun.",
      "zh": "看吧？我們不需要平板也能玩得開心。",
      "ja": "ほら？楽しいのにタブレットはいらないよ。",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Make a dog, daddy.",
      "zh": "做一隻狗，爸爸。",
      "ja": "犬を作って、パパ。",
      "time": "00:02:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's tell stories.",
      "zh": "我們來說故事吧。",
      "ja": "物語を話そう。",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just like camping.",
      "zh": "就像露營一樣。",
      "ja": "キャンプみたいにね。",
      "time": "00:03:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What kind of stories?",
      "zh": "什麼樣的故事？",
      "ja": "どんな話？",
      "time": "00:03:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Scary stories.",
      "zh": "恐怖故事。",
      "ja": "怖い話。",
      "time": "00:03:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not too scary.",
      "zh": "不要太恐怖。",
      "ja": "あまり怖くないの。",
      "time": "00:03:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How about adventure stories?",
      "zh": "冒險故事怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "冒険の話はどう？",
      "time": "00:03:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, I'll start.",
      "zh": "好，我來開始。",
      "ja": "うん、私が始めるね。",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Once upon a time, princess.",
      "zh": "從前，有位公主。",
      "ja": "昔々、お姫様がいました。",
      "time": "00:03:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, fine.",
      "zh": "好吧，行。",
      "ja": "わかった、いいよ。",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There was a brave princess.",
      "zh": "有一位勇敢的公主。",
      "ja": "勇敢なお姫様がいました。",
      "time": "00:03:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:03:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They traveled through dark forests and crossed big rivers.",
      "zh": "她們穿越黑暗森林，渡過大河。",
      "ja": "彼女たちは暗い森を旅し、大きな川を渡りました。",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did they find it?",
      "zh": "她們找到了嗎？",
      "ja": "見つけたの？",
      "time": "00:03:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:03:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And the treasure was friendship.",
      "zh": "寶藏是友誼。",
      "ja": "そして宝物は友情でした。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah, that's nice.",
      "zh": "啊，真好。",
      "ja": "ああ、それはいいね。",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's a perfect story for tonight.",
      "zh": "這是今晚完美的故事。",
      "ja": "今夜にぴったりの話だね。",
      "time": "00:03:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's build a fort for our indoor camping.",
      "zh": "我們來搭個堡壘，當作室內露營。",
      "ja": "室内キャンプのために砦を作ろう。",
      "time": "00:03:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, I'll get pillows.",
      "zh": "好，我去拿枕頭。",
      "ja": "うん、枕を取ってくる。",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This one goes here.",
      "zh": "這個放這裡。",
      "ja": "これはここに置く。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll get blankets.",
      "zh": "我去拿毯子。",
      "ja": "毛布を取ってくる。",
      "time": "00:03:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stack them here.",
      "zh": "堆在這裡。",
      "ja": "ここに積んで。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Coming.",
      "zh": "來了。",
      "ja": "行くよ。",
      "time": "00:03:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is heavy.",
      "zh": "這個很重。",
      "ja": "これは重い。",
      "time": "00:03:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let me help you both.",
      "zh": "讓我幫你們兩個。",
      "ja": "二人とも手伝うよ。",
      "time": "00:03:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's put this blanket over the chairs like a tent.",
      "zh": "我們把這條毯子蓋在椅子上，像帳篷。",
      "ja": "この毛布を椅子の上にかけてテントみたいにしよう。",
      "time": "00:03:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's like a cave.",
      "zh": "就像個洞穴。",
      "ja": "洞窟みたい。",
      "time": "00:04:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So cozy.",
      "zh": "好溫馨。",
      "ja": "とても居心地いい。",
      "time": "00:04:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Room for me?",
      "zh": "有我的位置嗎？",
      "ja": "私の場所ある？",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "有。",
      "ja": "あるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Coming.",
      "zh": "來了。",
      "ja": "行くよ。",
      "time": "00:04:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is the best fort ever.",
      "zh": "這是最棒的堡壘。",
      "ja": "これが今までで最高の砦だ。",
      "time": "00:04:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It really is.",
      "zh": "真的耶。",
      "ja": "本当にそうだね。",
      "time": "00:04:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Camping needs snacks.",
      "zh": "露營需要點心。",
      "ja": "キャンプにはおやつが必要だ。",
      "time": "00:04:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll make sandwiches.",
      "zh": "我來做三明治。",
      "ja": "サンドイッチを作るよ。",
      "time": "00:04:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "In the dark?",
      "zh": "在黑暗中？",
      "ja": "暗闇の中で？",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We have candles.",
      "zh": "我們有蠟燭。",
      "ja": "キャンドルがあるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I can see.",
      "zh": "我能看見。",
      "ja": "見えるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can I help?",
      "zh": "我可以幫忙嗎？",
      "ja": "手伝ってもいい？",
      "time": "00:04:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:04:31"
    },
    {
