      "ja": "じゃあ私は？",
      "time": "00:04:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good teamwork, everyone.",
      "zh": "大家合作得很好。",
      "ja": "みんなチームワークがいいね。",
      "time": "00:04:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Coming.",
      "zh": "來了。",
      "ja": "行くよ。",
      "time": "00:04:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't drop it.",
      "zh": "不要掉了。",
      "ja": "落とさないでね。",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is better than regular dinner.",
