      "time": "00:05:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is the best power outage ever.",
      "zh": "這是最棒的停電經驗。",
      "ja": "これまでで最高の停電だ。",
      "time": "00:05:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So comfy.",
      "zh": "好舒服。",
      "ja": "とても快適。",
      "time": "00:05:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Everyone comfortable?",
      "zh": "大家都舒服嗎？",
      "ja": "みんな快適？",
      "time": "00:05:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is so cool.",
