      "time": "00:05:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Really?",
      "zh": "真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本当に？",
      "time": "00:05:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You want to do it again?",
      "zh": "你想再玩一次？",
      "ja": "またやりたいの？",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No tablets, no TV.",
      "zh": "沒有平板，沒有電視。",
      "ja": "タブレットもテレビもなし。",
      "time": "00:05:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just us and the fort.",
      "zh": "只有我們和堡壘。",
      "ja": "僕たちと砦だけ。",
      "time": "00:05:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think that's a wonderful idea.",
      "zh": "我覺得那是個很棒的主意。",
      "ja": "それは素晴らしいアイデアだと思う。",
      "time": "00:05:58"
