    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That sounds like fun.",
      "zh": "聽起來很有趣。",
      "ja": "楽しそう。",
      "time": "00:06:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:06:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I love that.",
